Package: scrapeR
Type: Package
Title: ScrapeR Functions Fetch and Extract Text Content from Specified Web Pages
Version: 0.1.7
Authors@R: c(person("Mathieu Dubeau", email = "mdubeau20@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre", "cph")))
Description: The scrapeR function fetches and extracts text content from specified web pages. It handles HTTP errors and parses HTML efficiently. The function can handle hundreds of websites at a time using the 'in_batches' command.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
